{"id": "rios003", "name": "Cam_YazawaRI_494_12_25", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "... It's already 8 o'clock... It's been way too long\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "Object Shatters"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Wah! Who's there? \n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Ah... !</font>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "Footsteps "], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "You're... that Architect... Unit 10? \n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "... Hello Ms. Yazawa.\nArchitect No. OPCII_0584_X, at your command. \n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Command? No, I didn't want you to... What are you doing?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "I...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Is this... ?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "image", "attrs": ["rios0301"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "One of Dad's research plants... ?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "... I... was distracted when taking care of them... I am truly sorry!\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Distracted? Weird, this is the first time I've seen an Architect like this... Other Architects only follow orders.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "No... that's not true...\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "I knew it! You're different from other Architects I've met. You talk like a normal person, you hesitate, and you're even a bit afraid of me... Do you know what fear is?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "If you are referring to its definition... It means feeling terrified and disturbed...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "No, no, that's not what I meant.\nMy god, this is a huge discovery! I have to tell dad immediately...\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "... Wait, please don't!\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "Objects Crashing"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Wah! What's wrong?\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "I-I don't know what's going on with me, but... if anyone finds out about this, the system will determine that I am an error... <font size=\"1.6\">Then I will be destroyed...</font>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">Destroyed?</font>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Pl-please lower your voice! Ms. Yazawa!\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Oh, sorry... Is that true?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Yes... probably...\nI've been in this research institute for many years! I love this job, and I respect Dr. Yazawa... If it's possible... please keep my secret for me, please! \n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Um...\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "Eh? What are you doing here?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "Footsteps "], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Ah, Mom! You guys are done? Did it go well?\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "Not bad, today's data was pretty good... What's wrong? Aren't these the samples from the phase 2 plan? Why are they broken?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">... Uh...</font>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......\nMom, it was an accident... sorry.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "!?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "You did this? Why did you touch these plants?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "That, I thought this kind of flower was pretty. I thought after you're done with the experiment, I could use it to decorate my room... This Architect just happened to pass by!\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "... You should've asked in advance. That calendula has been injected with excessive endocrine and will wither away in 2 days, There's no point in bringing it back.   \n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Oh, got it... Ahahaha.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "If you want, I can buy you another one. Thankfully these samples' data have already been collected...\nArchitect, get rid of these things. \n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "... Command received, executing immediately.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "Rin, I can buy you the plant you want. As for the loss you cost the institute, it will be deducted from your allowance. Any problem with that?  \n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "... Oh... okay.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "...<i>*sigh*</i>...\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "Footsteps"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "... I am really sorry Ms. Yazawa, you took the blame for me...\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "It's alright, you won't be destroyed right? Don't sweat it, I'll keep the secret for you, no one will find out!  \n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Re-Really?\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Of course! But there's one condition.\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "Condition... ?\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Heehee... From now on, you'll have to call me by my name.\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "... Um, got it...\nThank you... Rin.\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……もう8時……おそいなぁ……\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "物が割れる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "きゃっ！だれ！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">あっ……！</font>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "あなたは……さっきのアーキテクト？\nえっと……10号機？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……矢澤さん、こんばんは。\nアーキテクトナンバーOPCII_0584_X、ご命令をお待ちしております。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "命令って……\n私は別に……あなたはここで何をしていたの？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "私は……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……これ……\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "image", "attrs": ["rios0301"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "これは……お父さんの植物？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……私……お世話をしてる時にうっかり……ごっごめんなさい！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "うっかり？\n変なの。そんなアーキテクト見たことない……\nだって他のアーキテクトは命令通りに仕事をするだけだもん。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……えっ……あ……そっそんなことは……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "やっぱり！\nあなたやっぱり他のアーキテクトと違う！\n話し方も人間みたいだもん。\n迷いがあるっていうか……私のことを怖がってる？\nあなた「怖い」って感情がわかるの？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "「怖い」という感情は……恐怖心や不安感を抱くことです……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "ちがうちがう！\nそういう意味じゃなくて！\nやだ、すごい大発見！\nはやくお父さんに知らせないと……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……待って！それはダメ！\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "物がぶつかる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "きゃっ！ど、どうしたの？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "わっ私も……どうして自分がこんなことになってるのかわかりません……\nでも……もしこのことが誰かにバレたら……私、システムにエラー認定されて……それで……<font size=\"1.6\">は、廃棄されちゃう……</font>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">廃棄！？</font>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "あのっ……！\n声のボリュームをもう少し下げてください……！矢澤さん！\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "あっ、ごめん……\nそれ、本当なの？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "お……おそらく……\nあのっ、私もうこの研究所に来てから長くて……っ！\nこの仕事が大好きで……っ！\n矢澤博士のことも尊敬してて……できれば……このことは秘密にしておいてほしいんです……お願いします！\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "うぅ……っ\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "あら？どうしてこんなところにいるの？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "あ、お母さん！\nもう終わったの？うまくいった？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "えぇ、今日はいいデータが取れたわ……あら？\nこれ、二期プランのサンプルじゃない。\nなんで割れてるの？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……それは……</font>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "………\n私が割っちゃったの……ごめんなさい。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "！？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "あなたがやったの？\nどうしてこれに触ったの。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "えっと……お花がきれいだなって……\nそれで、お母さんたちの研究が終わったら、お部屋に飾れないかなぁ～……なんて。\nあ！このアーキテクトはちょうど通りかかっただけだから！\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "……なら先にお母さんに聞きなさい。\nその花は多量の混合薬を打ってるから、2日も経てば枯れちゃうわよ。\nだから、持って帰っても意味ないの。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "そうだったんだ……あははは……\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "そんなに欲しいなら、新しいのを買ってあげるわ。\nここに置いてあるサンプルのデータは取り終えてたからいいものの……\nアーキテクト、これを片付けてちょうだい。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……承知いたしました。\n直ちに実行いたします。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "凛、花はお母さんが買ってあげる。\nでも、今回割ってしまった分はあなたのお小遣いから引くわよ。いいわね？\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "ぅえ～はぁい……\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "まったく……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "足音"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……ごめんなさい。\n矢澤さん、私のために……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "いいっていいって！\nこれであなたは廃棄されずに済むんでしょ？\n大丈夫！私あなたの秘密はちゃんと守るから！\n誰にも言わない！\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "ほ、本当ですか？\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "もちろん！\nでもね、ひとつだけ条件があるの。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "条件……ですか？\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "へへ……私のこと、名前で呼んで！\nそれから敬語もなし！\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……うん。わかった……\nありがとう……凛。\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……已經八點了……好久喔。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "物品摔碎"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "哇！是誰？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">啊……！</font>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "妳是……剛剛的建造者？……十號機？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……您好，矢澤小姐。\n建造者編號 OPCII_0584_X，聽候您的指令。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "指令？不，我沒有要妳……妳在做什麼？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……這是？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "image", "attrs": ["rios0301"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "是爸爸研究用的植物……？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……我……照顧它們時不小心分心了……真的很對不起！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "分心？好奇怪，我第一次看到建造者這樣……明明其他建造者都只會依照指令行動的。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……沒、沒這回事……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "果然！妳跟我遇過的其他建造者都不一樣，說話很像一般人，會猶豫，好像還有點怕我……妳知道害怕是什麼嗎？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "定義的話……是心中恐懼不安的意思……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "不不，我不是指那個啦。\n天啊，這是大發現！得趕快和爸爸說……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……等等，不要！\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "物品碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "哇！怎麼了？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我、我不知道自己是怎麼了，但是……這件事如果被其他人知道，系統會……會把我判定為異常，我會被……<font size=\"1.6\">銷毀……</font>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">銷毀！？</font>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "請、請小聲一些！矢澤小姐！\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "唔，對不起……妳說的是真的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "有……有可能……\n那個，我在這間研究所已經好多年了！我很喜歡這份工作，也很尊敬矢澤博士……可以的話……請您幫我保守秘密，拜託！\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "唔……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "嗯？妳怎麼在這種地方？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "啊，媽媽！妳們結束了？順利嗎？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "不錯，今天的數據不錯……怎麼回事？這不是二期計畫的樣本嗎？怎麼全碎了？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……那個……</font>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……。\n媽媽，是我不小心……對不起。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "！？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "是妳弄掉的？妳碰這些盆栽做什麼？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "那個，我覺得這種花很漂亮，想說如果妳們做完實驗了，可以用來裝飾我的房間……啊，這台建造者只是剛好經過而已！\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "……妳這孩子也不先問一下。那盆金盞花施打了過量的混合激素，兩天內就會完全枯萎，帶回去也沒意義啊。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "原來是這樣……啊哈哈哈。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "妳想要的話，我再另外買一盆給妳吧。還好這些樣本的數據都收集完了……\n建造者，把這些東西處理掉。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……已收到指令，即刻執行。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "凜，妳想要的盆栽我可以買給妳。至於研究所的損失，就從零用錢裡扣。有沒有問題？\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "嗚嗚……沒有。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "唉……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……真不好意思，矢澤小姐，妳為了我……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "沒關係啦，這樣就不會被銷毀了吧？放心，我會幫妳保守秘密，不讓任何人知道！\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "真、真的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "當然！不過我有條件。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "條件……？\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "嘻嘻……從現在開始，妳要用名字叫我。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……嗯，我知道了……\n謝謝妳……凜。\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "...벌써 8신데... 늦네.\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "물건이 부서진다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "으앗! 누구세요?\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">이런......!</font>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "당신은... 방금 그 아키텍트? ....10호기?\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "안녕하십니까, Yazawa 씨.\n넘버링 OPCII_0584_X 아키텍트입니다. 지령을 내려주세요.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "지령? 아니, 난 딱히 내릴 지령이 없는데... 지금 뭐하고 있는 거야?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "저는...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "...이건?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "image", "attrs": ["rios0301"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "아빠가 연구하던 식물...?\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "...제가...잘 지키고 있었는데 순간 실수로 방심한 사이에... 정말 죄송합니다!\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "방심? 신기하네, 아키텍트가 이런 모습을 보이는 거...다른 아키텍트는 모두 지령에 따라서만 움직이는데.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "...그, 그건...\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "역시! 넌 내가 봤던 다른 아키텍트랑 어딘가 다른 것 같아! 말하는 것도 엄청 사람같고. 뭔가 주저하는 것이...꼭 나를 무서워하는 것 같은데... 혹시 무섭다는 것이 뭔지 알아?\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "해당 말의 정의로는... 마음 속에 공포로 인한 불안감을 뜻합니다...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "아니, 그 뜻이 아니라고.\n세상에, 이건 엄청난 대발견이야! 빨리 아빠한테 말해줘야...\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "...잠깐, 안 됩니다!\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "물건이 부딪힌다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "앗! 무슨 일이지?\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "저, 저도 제가 왜 이렇게 행동하는지 모르겠습니다만... 이 일을 만약 다른 누군가가 알게 된다면, 시스템은 아마....제게서 큰 오류가 생겼다는 것으로 간주하고 그렇게 되면 저는... <font size=\"1.6\">폐기될 겁니다...</font>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">폐, 폐기라고!?</font>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "목, 목소리를 좀 낮춰주십시오! Yazawa 씨!\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "아, 미안... 네가 말한 게 사실이야?\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "아.... 아마도 그럴 겁니다...\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "윽......\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "응? 네가 왜 여기에 있니?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "아, 엄마! 이제 끝난 거야? 잘 끝났어?\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "뭐, 나름대로. 오늘 데이터가 꽤 괜찮... 무슨 일이지? 이건 2분기 프로젝트 때 샘플이잖아? 어째서 전부 엉망으로...?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">...그게...</font>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......\n엄마, 내가 실수로 그랬어... 미안.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "!?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "네가 그랬다고? 이걸로 뭘 하려고 했던 거니!\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "그게, 꽃이 너무 이뻐서...만약 두 사람 실험 끝나면 내 방에 둬볼까 하는 생각을 하고....아, 이 아키텍트는 그냥 지나가던 것뿐이야!\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "...그랬으면 먼저 물어봤어야지. 이 꽃은 혼합 호르몬이 과다하게 투여돼서 어차피 집으로 가지고 가봤자 2일도 안 돼서 시들고 말 거야.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "그렇구나....아하하하.\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "그래도 가지고 싶으면, 엄마가 다른 거 사다가 하나 방에 놔줄게. 다행히 이 샘플의 데이터를 모두 모아놨기에 망정이지...\n아키텍트, 이것들 좀 치워줘.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "...지령을 명 받았습니다. 즉시 수행하겠습니다.\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "Rin, 네가 원하는 화분은 엄마가 사다 줄게. 대신에 연구소에 있는 물건을 못 쓰게 만들었으니, 그 부분은 용돈에서 제외할 줄 알아. 문제 있니?\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "흐흐흑... 알았어.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "휴...\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "발걸음"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "...정말 죄송합니다, Yazawa 씨. 저를 위해서...\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "괜찮아~ 이렇게 하면 폐기 안 되는 거지? 절대 아무한테도 말 안 하고 꼭 비밀 지켜줄게!\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "저, 정말입니까?\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "물론이지! 하지만 조건이 있어.\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "조건...?\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "히히히... 앞으로는 날 부를 때, 이름을 불러주도록. 그리고 존댓말도 쓰지 않기!\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "....네... 아니, 알겠어...\n고마워.... Rin.\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……已經八點了……好久喔。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "物品摔碎"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "哇！是誰？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">啊……！</font>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "妳是……剛剛的建造者？……十號機？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……您好，矢澤小姐。\n建造者編號 OPCII_0584_X，聽候您的指令。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "指令？不，我沒有要妳……妳在做什麼？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……這是？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "image", "attrs": ["rios0301"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "是爸爸研究用的植物……？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……