"type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……。\n媽媽，是我不小心……對不起。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "！？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "是妳弄掉的？妳碰這些盆栽做什麼？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "那個，我覺得這種花很漂亮，想說如果妳們做完實驗了，可以用來裝飾我的房間……啊，這台建造者只是剛好經過而已！\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "……妳這孩子也不先問一下。那盆金盞花施打了過量的混合激素，兩天內就會完全枯萎，帶回去也沒意義啊。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "原來是這樣……啊哈哈哈。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "妳想要的話，我再另外買一盆給妳吧。還好這些樣本的數據都收集完了……\n建造者，把這些東西處理掉。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……已收到指令，即刻執行。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "凜，妳想要的盆栽我可以買給妳。至於研究所的損失，就從零用錢裡扣。有沒有問題？\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "嗚嗚……沒有。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "唉……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "腳步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……真不好意思，矢澤小姐，妳為了我……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "沒關係啦，這樣就不會被銷毀了吧？放心，我會幫妳保守秘密，不讓任何人知道！\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "真、真的嗎？\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "當然！不過我有條件。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "條件……？\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "嘻嘻……從現在開始，妳要用名字叫我。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……嗯，我知道了……\n謝謝妳……凜。\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Mute"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……已经八点了……好久喔。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "物品摔碎"], "content": ""}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "哇！是谁？\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["???"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">啊……！ </font>\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "脚步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "妳是……刚刚的建造者？ ……十号机？\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……您好，矢泽小姐。\n建造者编号 OPCII_0584_X，听候您的指令。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "指令？不，我没有要妳……妳在做什么？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……这是？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "image", "attrs": ["rios0301"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "是爸爸研究用的植物……？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……我……照顾它们时不小心分心了……真的很对不起！\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "分心？好奇怪，我第一次看到建造者这样……明明其他建造者都只会依照指令行动的。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……没、没这回事……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "果然！妳跟我遇过的其他建造者都不一样，说话很像一般人，会犹豫，好像还有点怕我……妳知道害怕是什么吗？\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "定义的话……是心中恐惧不安的意思……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "不不，我不是指那个啦。\n天啊，这是大发现！得赶快和爸爸说……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……等等，不要！\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Crash_Obj_01", "物品碰撞"], "content": ""}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "哇！怎么了？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "我、我不知道自己是怎么了，但是……这件事如果被其他人知道，系统会……会把我判定为异常，我会被……<font size=\"1.6\">销毁……</font>\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"3.6\">销毁！ ？ </font>\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "请、请小声一些！矢泽小姐！\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "唔，对不起……妳說的是真的吗？\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "有……有可能……\n那个，我在这间研究所已经好多年了！我很喜欢这份工作，也很尊敬矢泽博士……可以的话……请您帮我保守秘密，拜托！\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "唔……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "嗯？妳怎么在这种地方？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "脚步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "啊，妈妈！妳们结束了？顺利吗？\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "不错，今天的数据不错……怎么回事？这不是二期计画的样本吗？怎么全碎了？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">……那个……</font>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……。\n妈妈，是我不小心……对不起。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "！ ？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "是妳弄掉的？妳碰这些盆栽做什么？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "那个，我觉得这种花很漂亮，想说如果妳们做完实验了，可以用来装饰我的房间……啊，这台建造者只是刚好经过而已！\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "……妳这孩子也不先问一下。那盆金盏花施打了过量的混合激素，两天内就会完全枯萎，带回去也没意义啊。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "原来是这样……啊哈哈哈。\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "妳想要的话，我再另外买一盆给妳吧。还好这些样本的数据都收集完了……\n建造者，把这些东西处理掉。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……已收到指令，即刻执行。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "凛，妳想要的盆栽我可以买给妳。至于研究所的损失，就从零用钱里扣。有没有问题？\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "呜呜……没有。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Asa"], "content": "唉……\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Step_3", "脚步"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……真不好意思，矢泽小姐，妳为了我……\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "没关系啦，这样就不会被销毁了吧？放心，我会帮妳保守秘密，不让任何人知道！\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "真、真的吗？\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "当然！不过我有条件。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "条件……？\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "嘻嘻……从现在开始，妳要用名字叫我。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["OPCII_0584_X"], "content": "……嗯，我知道了……\n谢谢妳……凛。\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[讯号中断]</i>\n"}]]}